dct_description_sm: Title from disc label.  Title handwritten.

Includes ADM1, ADM2, and ADM3 administrative units and capitals for Pakistan, current as of the 1998 Pakistan census, finalized November, 2004. The spatial data are geo-referenced in decimal degrees using the WGS84 Spheroid, and incorporate DCW coastlines and international boundaries.
System requirements: IBM or compatible computer; CD-ROM drive; software capable of reading an ESRI shapefile, such as ArcGIS.
